- cs.DB (Databases) is likely because the paper discusses uniform equivalence, which is a well-known concept in deductive databases.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is likely because the paper discusses logic programming and program optimization.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible because the paper analyzes the computational complexity of the different notions of equivalence.
